                  </decoDesc>
                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#156vc">f. 156vc</locus>
                           <desc>: Note on the number of books in possession of the church.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#156vc">156vc</locus>: ኍልቈ፡ መጻሕፍት፡ ዘደብረ፡ ገነት፡ መካነ፡
                              ቅድስት፡ ኪዳነ፡ ምሕርት፡ ፴ወ፯።</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en">
                              <locus target="#156vc">156vc</locus>: The number of books of Dabra
                              Gannat Makāna Qǝddǝst Kidāna Mǝḥrat is 47.</quote>
                           <note> Written in a more recent hand. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#157ra">ff. 157ra-158</locus>
                           <desc>va: Homily on the Lord's Prayer, ascribed to John Chrysostom,
                              incomplete. </desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           <note> The text is written in uneven, irregular script. Cp. BN Ms. éth.
                              157, no. 3 (ZotBNat 257-58). </note>
                        </item>
